{"tid":2188454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母死其士","createTime":"2020-09-04T08:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T03:46:24.000Z","uid":103920,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6067323ea3ec012ff39f5ca429611a3735dedc1f","tid":2188454,"uid":103920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"之前政府公布升降機從業員可以免費做病毒測試，之後推左成個禮拜都無人願意做，死都要延長日子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okDR1dq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokDR1dq.jpg&h=933eaa30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直到今日，屌你老母其士為左幫政府谷大檢測人數，向每個伙計派晒樽，又要點名、Mark低晒邊個仲未做，務求個個都要【自願】做測試。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrzqmdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrzqmdE.jpg&h=e5e58a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦垃圾其士，依家都已經有全民檢測，點解仲要透過公司同政府做檢測呀？出賣公司員工好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3c94b7e6abcc47f631a1614572f3fc3cb595b6","tid":2188454,"uid":103920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf3a31211a402f26a8593b9ca7afbfda194241de","tid":2188454,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite